00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:58,880
That's all for today's class.
今天的课就到这里。

24
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:07,200
We will continue our lecture on crime and punishment tomorrow.
明天我们会继续讲关于犯罪与惩罚的讲座。

