They mentioned juvenile offenders.
他们提到了未成年罪犯。

60
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:07,720
All right, so let's look at these two words because, well, offender can be pretty general.
好的，让我们看看这两个词，因为“罪犯”这个词可以很宽泛。

61
