00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:38,080
people, younger children or teenagers, they don't really understand the law.
年幼的孩子或青少年，他们并不真正理解法律。

73
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:41,040
They don't really understand crime or good and bad.
他们并不真正理解犯罪或好坏。

74
