So it should be easier on them.
所以应该对他们宽松一些。

75
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,880
All right, very good.
好的，非常好。

76
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:50,040
So we have juvenile offenders and we also have wrongful conviction.
所以我们有未成年罪犯，还有冤假错案。

77
