That happened.
那确实发生了。

85
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,280
Right.
对。

86
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:18,160
But it's a wrongful conviction if Marco didn't really steal a computer but we decided that
但如果Marco并没有真的偷电脑，而我们却认定他偷了，那就是冤假错案。

87
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,160
he did.


88
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,160
Okay.
好的。

89
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,920
So it was a wrong decision.
所以这是一个错误的决定。

90
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,920
Right.
对。

91
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:27,520
